{"tid":180410,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"籃球問題 帶波撞人同阻人前進","createTime":"2017-03-31T02:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T05:25:24.000Z","uid":80050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32ef814331f8c3b5c4d3fe4c6e662f513fa84437","tid":180410,"uid":80050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"有冇ching可以比個清晰的指引我?<br />\n問fd就個個都唔同意見<br />\n我既理解係應該防守攞好位,可以向左,右, 後方移動黎保持合法防守位置， 之後如果進攻方撞到防守方的身體主幹部位(胸口位置), 就係charging。如果防守向前移動 / 傾前跳起，之後的撞擊就係阻擋犯規。 如果防守垂直跳起，撞擊就當無事。而如果撞擊時係處於免責區 (籃下半圓), 就點都係阻擋犯規。<br />\n<br />\n我有冇理解錯？<br />\n<br />\n有人話撞擊時如果進玫方係射緊波 / 傳緊波就當無事?<br />\n有人話要call charging 一定要撞到訓低埋先計?<br />\n有人話街場同正式籃球唔同，街場（3 on 3 / 5 on 5)點都唔會計charging，比賽先計?<br />\n有冇ching可以比個清晰的指引黎，最好有例子。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33715e8e1e6c54b645125b2d96b2b1fa6df68a07","tid":180410,"uid":84579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:06:43.000Z","msg":"街場基本上都無charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打咗十幾年波都無見過"},{"pid":"7591538e8a8d10dafb1a6f34f328c9d6979f783a","tid":180410,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>街場基本上都無charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打咗十幾年波都無見過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> +1"},{"pid":"728ab000402b6a225ce083b1ae88cf43f5606c8c","tid":180410,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:07:36.000Z","msg":"你咪試下係街場叫charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06587df18b5c180728ed541dcd64123f617a27b0","tid":180410,"uid":5014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:07:56.000Z","msg":"打藍球根本就係鬥撞<br />\n帶波撞贏就冇事 撞輸就foul<br />\n街場 比賽都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7366c04b4e96e3c1028de6658c953bc4fac931d","tid":180410,"uid":62710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"主要睇防守方企定未<br />\n企定左先撞埋黎咪charging囉<br />\n隻腳仲郁緊就blocking喇"},{"pid":"7693f1c4e54c26afb27eaa7a8fe123f6b8a0401a","tid":180410,"uid":80050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>街場基本上都無charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打咗十幾年波都無見過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇charging去保護防守方，Ｄ大隻佬既亂撞起黎咪屈晒？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec25c9e8d729a497214bb7e6a4b845e673fc0d5","tid":180410,"uid":80050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪試下係街場叫charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後會點?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7bf4b344751b3dfeebf6c32a9d01c0352c3d309","tid":180410,"uid":80050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主要睇防守方企定未<br />\n企定左先撞埋黎咪charging囉<br />\n隻腳仲郁緊就blocking喇</blockquote><br />\nD人話唔計charging喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77ab5dddae149fc4fe5a7970fdcd9568597df49","tid":180410,"uid":9217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>街場基本上都無charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打咗十幾年波都無見過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇charging去保護防守方，Ｄ大隻佬既亂撞起黎咪屈晒？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n街場係咁架啦<br />\nfoul都係自己叫 想黑死你幾時都得添<br />\n以前跟隊個時見過人會foul charging同阻人前進<br />\n成個場都係到屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fad0398229166afdf99d7f1d8b28779eaa1767","tid":180410,"uid":80050