lyTime":"2017-03-31T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>街場基本上都無charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打咗十幾年波都無見過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇charging去保護防守方，Ｄ大隻佬既亂撞起黎咪屈晒？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n街場係咁架啦<br />\nfoul都係自己叫 想黑死你幾時都得添<br />\n以前跟隊個時見過人會foul charging同阻人前進<br />\n成個場都係到屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有冇原因點解街場先唔計charging?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係人身安全既問題</blockquote><br />\n因為香港街場除咗鳩撞同跳投冇其他打法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實最主要係進攻犯規係好爭議性嘅，你覺得有，人地好多都覺得無，又無replay,又唔係正規比賽咁有個球證做最後裁決，口同鼻拗，講得黎都球場熄燈唔洗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁不如有個潛規則，係公平地雙方都冇charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf676a62fa7b1ba218ca6f85d5d4176169125bea","tid":180410,"uid":80050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>街場基本上都無charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打咗十幾年波都無見過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇charging去保護防守方，Ｄ大隻佬既亂撞起黎咪屈晒？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n街場係咁架啦<br />\nfoul都係自己叫 想黑死你幾時都得添<br />\n以前跟隊個時見過人會foul charging同阻人前進<br />\n成個場都係到屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有冇原因點解街場先唔計charging?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係人身安全既問題</blockquote><br />\n因為香港街場除咗鳩撞同跳投冇其他打法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實最主要係進攻犯規係好爭議性嘅，你覺得有，人地好多都覺得無，又無replay,又唔係正規比賽咁有個球證做最後裁決，口同鼻拗，講得黎都球場熄燈唔洗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁不如有個潛規則，係公平地雙方都冇charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nso sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw，當我打正式比賽，我上面對帶波撞人同阻人前進既理解岩唔岩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8107d0c66823f976acbe541e38c3b0fca6992f74","tid":180410,"uid":28796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:30:21.000Z","msg":"巴打們<br />\n我想順便問下，<br />\n如果我mark緊人，自然雙脾係打開啦，<br />\n咁對方想過我時，我釘死隻腳，佢衝過嚟kick到我隻腳，<br />\n咁我有無犯規？<br />\n我雙腳無郁過，只係mak開企到實一實。<br />\n唔該"},{"pid":"fd1f01e2dbac71c8fb44f2307946408ff1e44858","tid":180410,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"唔使搞到咁複雜，總之睇碰撞前一刻防守者企定未(最好訓低埋) <br />\n撞個吓先企定就計阻人<br />\n當然如果攻方夾硬用膊頭/手大動作頂開人就唔使企定都有charging<br />\n<br />\n另外街場唔係無charging, 只係無球證廢事特登搏同埋廢事訓地， 如果你企定定人地都照直撞埋嚟你都可以試吓call既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見過有人咁做，不過對面一定唔多gur<br />\n亦都見過攻方自己撞左埋個企定既人度知衰比對面開"},{"pid":"599c027b2c5ed9df117240b38089e0c939a7f014","tid":180410,"uid":7865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"街場裝咩charging<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n9衝埋嚟咪縮囉 打nba咩屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e4bbc314407bfb7160671db4bfef9ba6a0557a","tid":180410,"uid":86051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打們<br />\n我想順便問下，<br />\n如果我mark緊人，自然雙脾係打開啦，<br />\n咁對方想過我時，我釘死隻腳，佢衝過嚟kick到我隻腳，<br />\n咁我有無犯規？<br />\n我雙腳無郁過，只係mak開企到實一實。<br />\n唔該</blockquote><br />\n應該有<br />\n個身唔到淨係出腳就算係佢kick到多數都會吹"},{"pid":"ff3c00c8913ebcc0d2a387d5d68fe3a65e71bbb7","tid":180410,"uid":86051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:39:45.0